   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address">
            <address>
               <addrLine>
                  <pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3167_0046"/>Herrn Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine>
               <addrLine>
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>
               </addrLine>
               <addrLine>
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb397">IX. Frankgaſse 1.</rs>
               </addrLine>
            </address>
         </div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1">
            <opener>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="pre-print">
                     <rs type="place" ref="#pmb51377">Wagner-Theater</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p rend="center">
                  <pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3167_0045"/>
                  <hi rend="pre-print">Gruss aus <rs type="place" ref="#pmb734">Bayreuth</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
            </opener>
            <p>Viele treue Grüße, <salute rend="inline">liebſter Freund!</salute> Und bald ſehen wir
               uns in <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02821-1"/>
               <hi rend="latintype">
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Ischl</rs>
               </hi>
               <note type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02821-1h">Zwischen <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1897-08-19" subtype="date-only"/> und <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1897-08-30" subtype="date-only"/> waren <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> und <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> beide in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</rs>.</note>,
               nicht wahr? Nachrichten treffen mich bis Ende der Woche in <hi rend="latintype">
                  <rs type="place" ref="#pmb401">Muenchen, Hotel Marienbad</rs>
               </hi>.</p>
            <closer>Dein <lb/>
               <signed>Paul Goldmann</signed>
            </closer>
         </div>
      </body>
